CSS: Cascading Style Sheet: 
Cascading Style Sheets (CSS) is a stylesheet language used to describe the presentation of a document written in HTML or XML (including XML dialects such as SVG, MathML or XHTML). CSS describes how elements should be rendered on screen, on paper, in speech, or on other media.

HTML, XML:
<html>
<body>
<h1>
<p>

https://www.w3.org/Style/CSS/#specs

https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Learn/CSS/First_steps/What_is_CSS

ruleset: 

color:"red"
background-color:"blue"
font-size: 20px; 
font-family: 'Arial'

3 Ways to connect CSS with HTML: 
1) Inline CSS - Not Advisable
2) Internal CSS - Not recommended
3) External CSS


INLINE CSS: 
<html>
<head>
</head>
<body>
<h1 style="color:white; background-color:lightgrey;font-size:30px;"> Its a rainy day </h1>
</body>
</html>

INTERNAL CSS: 
<html>
<head>
<style>
h1
{
color:white; 
background-color:lightgrey;
font-size:30px;
}
</style>
</head>
<body>
<h1> Its a rainy day </h1>

<h1> Its a rainy day </h1>

<h1> Its a rainy day </h1>

<h1> Its a rainy day </h1>
</body>
</html>
-----------------
<html>
<head>
<style>
h1, h2
{
color:white; 
background-color:lightgrey;
font-size:30px;
}
</style>
</head>
<body>
<h1> Its a rainy day </h1>

<h2> Its a rainy day </h2>

<h1> Its a rainy day </h1>

<h1> Its a rainy day </h1>
</body>
</html>
----------

style.css: 

h1
{
color:yellow; 
background-color: blue; 
}

<html>
<head>
<link rel="stylesheet" href="style.css">
</head>
<body>
<h1> Its a rainy day </h1>
<h2> Its a rainy day </h2>
<h1> Its a rainy day </h1>
<h1> Its a rainy day </h1>
</body>
</html>
--------------
font-family, font-weight, font-style

p
{
color:yellow; 
background-color: blue; 
font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;
font-weight:bold; 
font-style: italic;
}

--------
p
{
color:yellow; 
background-color: blue; 
font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;
font-weight:bold; 
font-style: italic;
text-transform:capitalize; /*uppercase, lowercase*/
}
----------
span
{
text-decoration:overline;/*underline,overline,line-through */
}
<html>
<head>
<link rel="stylesheet" href="style.css">
</head>
<body>
<p> Pariyerum perumal <span>B.A.,B.L.,</span> </p>
</body>
</html>
------------
p
{
text-align:right; /*center, justify, left, right */
}

<html>
<head>
<link rel="stylesheet" href="style.css">
</head>
<body>
